data.description: Come check out this Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in Pinson offers a wonderful open floor plan perfect for entertaining. It boasts a well designed kitchen with granite countertops and stainless appliances and generous amounts of storage. You will love the spacious master suite which includes a master bath with separate tub and shower and large walk-in closet. The neighborhood pool and clubhouse are available for your enjoyment. Seller will contribute a Buyer credit at closing. Please call Listing Agent for more details. Jefferson County, Clay-Chalkville Schools. Very convenient to shopping and dining as well as easy access to I-59 and I-459.
